data.title: Eagles press conference live featuring Chase Daniel, Rodney McLeod, Ron Brooks (VIDEO)
data.meta_description: The new Birds are facing the press.
data.text:
The Philadelphia Eagles are holding a press conference today, Thursday, March 10 at 3:30 PM ET to introduce some of their NFL free agency new signings. The following three players are scheduled to speak: quarterback Chase Daniel, safety Rodney McLeod, and cornerback Ron Brooks. Eagles head coach Doug Pederson and executive vice president of football operations are also scheduled to speak. Watch the press conference in the video above this post (courtesy of PhiladelphiaEagles.com).
